{"prompt": "Create a digital hub for a local historical landmark. The branding should include a dignified saffron yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Pioneer's Rest Historical Landmark</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f5f5dc; /* Off-white background */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #daa520; /* Saffron Yellow */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #b8860b; /* Darker Saffron for headings */\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #daa520;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(218, 165, 32, 0.7), rgba(218, 165, 32, 0.7)), url('landmark_placeholder.jpg'); /* Placeholder image with saffron overlay */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .section img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 3px solid #daa520;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #daa520; /* Saffron Yellow */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            background-color: #fff8dc; /* Cornsilk, a lighter shade */\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #b8860b; /* Darker Saffron */\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #8b4513; /* Saddle Brown, a complementary darker shade */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Pioneer's Rest Historical Landmark</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#history\">Our History</a>\n        <a href=\"#visit\">Plan Your Visit</a>\n        <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n        <a href=\"#support\">Support Us</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Step Back in Time</h1>\n        <p>Discover the rich heritage and stories of Pioneer's Rest.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\n        <section id=\"history\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Rich History</h2>\n            <p>Pioneer's Rest stands as a testament to the resilience and vision of the early settlers who shaped our community. Established in 1872, this iconic landmark has witnessed generations of change, preserving the echoes of the past for the future.</p>\n            <img src=\"placeholder_history.jpg\" alt=\"Historical photo of Pioneer's Rest\">\n            <p>From its humble beginnings as a central gathering point to its current status as a cherished heritage site, the story of Pioneer's Rest is woven into the fabric of our town's identity. Learn about the key figures, pivotal events, and the architectural evolution that makes this place so special.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"visit\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Plan Your Visit</h2>\n            <p>We invite you to explore Pioneer's Rest and immerse yourself in history. Whether you're a local resident or a visitor, there's something to captivate everyone.</p>\n            <h3>Hours of Operation</h3>\n            <p>Tuesday - Sunday: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM<br>\n            Closed on Mondays and major holidays.</p>\n            <h3>Admission</h3>\n            <p>Adults: $10<br>\n            Seniors (65+): $8<br>\n            Children (6-12): $5<br>\n            Children under 6: Free</p>\n            <h3>Location</h3>\n            <p>123 Heritage Lane, Old Town, CA 90210</p>\n            <p>Contact us at <a href=\"mailto:info@pioneersrest.org\" style=\"color: #8b4513;\">info@pioneersrest.org</a> or call (555) 123-4567.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"gallery\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Gallery</h2>\n            <p>A glimpse into the beauty and historical significance of Pioneer's Rest.</p>\n            <img src=\"placeholder_gallery1.jpg\" alt=\"Exterior view of the landmark\">\n            <img src=\"placeholder_gallery2.jpg\" alt=\"Interior detail of the landmark\">\n            <img src=\"placeholder_gallery3.jpg\" alt=\"Artifact from the landmark\">\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"support\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Support Our Mission</h2>\n            <p>Pioneer's Rest is a non-profit organization dedicated to preserving this vital piece of our history. Your support helps us maintain the landmark, develop educational programs, and share its stories with future generations.</p>\n            <p>Consider becoming a member, making a donation, or volunteering your time. Every contribution makes a difference!</p>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                <button style=\"background-color: #daa520; color: #fff; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 1.1em; cursor: pointer;\">Donate Now</button>\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Pioneer's Rest Historical Landmark. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll-to-section functionality for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}